<p>I have made that iced coffee.  it is a treat to wander downstairs in the country too early for anyone else to be awake on a summer Saturday, get it out of the refrigerator, put it through a coffee filter into a French jelly glass, add the milk, and step onto the front porch to sit alone sipping coffee and looking at the fields and the mountains.</p>
<p>It&#39;s good to spend a little time in heaven before the day starts.</p>
<p>May all your summer dreams come true!</p>
