    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>We just left Seattle after an 11 day trip and we LOVED the cooler weather (leaving the 100 degree Virginia heat behind us).  Our favorite Seattle &#8220;summer&#8221; moments were when we spent a few days at a beach cottage on Vashon Island and grilled walla walla sweets for our burgers and snacked on GIGANTIC sugar snap peas.  We put strawberries on everything for dessert and sipped a nice oregon pinot noir under blankets while the kids poked at the washed up jelly fish and sea cucumbers during low tide.  A perfect summer if you ask me.</p>
