    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I love your new feeling about posting here, and I have a feeling I&#39;ll love reading people&#39;s summer lists when I make my way through the comments!  Orangette has been one of my very favorite spots for a very long time now and I&#39;m glad it&#39;s feeling fresh for you! </p>
<p>Made some popsicles last week: made a basil lemon simple syrup and when it cooled a whirred some of it in the blender with wild blackberries and a little yogurt.  So delicious.  Maybe a little less sugar next time.</p>
<p>p.s. Oh, I haven&#39;t had a Gordon&#39;s Cup yet this summer!  Must do that.</p>
